captures-a-martian-day-from-dawn-to-dusk/">NASA</a>称，在 11 月中旬合相开始前几天，好奇号接到指示记录 12 小时的序列。这个想法是为了看看它是否能够捕捉到可能出现的任何天气事件。虽然这最终没有发生，但好奇号 11 月 8 日拍摄的图像仍然非常迷人。它们被拼凑成两个视频，展示了其前后危险摄像头的视图。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>好奇号的危险摄像头通常用于帮助驾驶员避开可能对火星车造成危险的地形。但由于漫游车在 11 月 11 日至 25 日暂停执行任务之前停了下来，相机被腾出来进行一些观光。好奇号从早上 5:30 到下午 5:30 在火星夏普山底部的位置进行了记录。它和其他火星探测器此后恢复了正常活动。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-12/ecd98d00-a804-11ee-bf7f-acb7d70341ee" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-12/ecd98d00-a804-11ee-bf7f-acb7d70341ee" style="height:1024px;width:1024px;" alt="好奇号后置摄像头拍摄的火星一天的延时摄影" data-uuid="6452c22b-4e5b-3d01-af79-d3a97482dbcb"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> NASA/JPL-加州理工学院</div></figure><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/nasas-curiosity-rover-snapped-this-dreamy-timelapse-of-a-martian-day-175701537.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/nasas-curiosity-rover-snapped-this-dreamy-timelapse-of-a-martian-day-175701537.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 01a7c0af-f638-4688-b2ea-4294cfb84e4f </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Cheyenne MacDonald]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Sun, 31 Dec 2023 17:57:01 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1704045576</ingested><modified> 2023-12-31T17:59:41+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Science]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Cheyenne MacDonald]]></category><media:content height="958" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F8bee7460-a804-11ee-8bff-275c5d23790d&amp;resi