> Vizio <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.refreshrateclassaction.com/docs/2023.11.09%20-%20Second%20Amended%20VIZIO%20Settlement%20Agreement%20(signed%20by%20Ps).pdf" data-original-link="https://www.refreshrateclassaction.com/docs/2023.11.09%20-%20Second%20Amended%20VIZIO%20Settlement%20Agreement%20(signed%20by%20Ps).pdf"><ins>否认自己有任何不当行为</ins></a>，但同意以 300 万美元和解，涵盖在加利福尼亚州购买的所有带有上述描述的广告的 Vizio 电视，时间可追溯到 2014 年 4 月 30 日，直至法院最终判决。最终批准听证会目前定于 2024 年 6 月 20 日举行。人们可能有权获得最高 50 美元的付款，但索赔必须在 2024 年 3 月 30 日之前提交。索赔表可<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.refreshrateclassaction.com/Home/ClaimForm" data-original-link="https://www.refreshrateclassaction.com/Home/ClaimForm">在此处</a>找到。 Vizio 还同意停止以这种方式营销其电视，并“向所有和解集体成员提供增强的服务和有限的一年保修。”</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/some-vizio-tv-owners-can-claim-a-share-of-a-3-million-settlement-over-misleading-marketing-220925933 .html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/some-vizio-tv-owners-can-claim-a-share-of-a-3-million-settlement-over-misleading-marketing-220925933.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 63591f17-fb0c-40c6-b8fe-1ce12d415bf3 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Cheyenne MacDonald]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Sat, 30 Dec 2023 22:09:25 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1703974166</ingested><modified> 2023-12-30T22:09:29+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[Company Legal & Law Matters]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Cheyenne MacDonald]]></category><media:content height="826" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Ffffe62d0-a75e-11ee-befe-a40335307a55&amp;resize=1400%2C826&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=44161d21cbbac8129236843ea585d95aa821e14b" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="826" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Ffffe62d0-a75e-11ee-befe-a40335307a55&amp;resize=1400%2C826&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=ad555dba992b519c4b5e8081ab9c58ccffdf8d27" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Vizio]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A vizio V series tv]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Vizio V series TV]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Now’s the last chance to send your name to one of Jupiter’s moons on NASA’s Europa Clipper]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>美国宇航局为一种“瓶子里的信息”收集名字的活动将在本周末后结束，该活动将随即将到来的欧罗巴快艇任务一起飞行，所以如果你希望参与但尚未提交，你最好抓紧时间起来并这样做。这些签名将伴随着美国桂冠诗人阿达·利蒙为欧罗巴写的一首诗，这首诗将以利蒙的笔迹刻在附在航天器上的金属板上。木星最大的卫星之一木卫二被认为在其冰冷的地壳下有一个深咸水海洋，那里的条件可能适合微生物生命。</p><p>要参加瓶中信活动，您只需访问<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://europa.nasa.gov/message-in-a-bottle/sign-on/" data-original-link="https://europa.nasa.gov/message-in-a-bottle/sign-on/">NASA 网站</a>并填写一份简短的注册表即可。截止日期是明天，即 12 月 31 日。到目前为止，已有超过 240 万人添加了自己的名字。据 NASA 称，每个参与者的名字都将被用模板以极小的字母印在微芯片上，使用电子束可以创建小于人类头发宽度 1/1000 的文本行。这些微芯片将被贴在包含这首诗的盘子上。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="bed93c429185468796ee71705cbf6cbf"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/EgWbeDNPD6o?rel=0&amp;start=1" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div><p>欧罗巴快船飞船计划于 2024 年 10 月发射，距离到达木星轨道还需要六年时间。一旦到达那里，它将通过一系列近距离飞越来调查木卫二的潜在宜居性。木卫二是估计有 95 颗环绕木星的卫星之一，也是人类已知最长的卫星之一。</p><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/nows-the-last-chance-to-send-your-name-to-one-of-jupiters-moons-on-nasas-europa-clipper -181639628.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/nows-the-last-chance-to-send-your-name-to-one-of-jupiters-moons-on-nasas-europa-clipper-181639628.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4298502c-2778-408e-be99-3af8e6867760 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Cheyenne MacDonald]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Sat, 30 Dec 2023 18:16:39 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1703974274</ingested><modified> 2023-12-30T22:11:17+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Science]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Cheyenne MacDonald]]></category><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Fd02f6f30-a73c-11ee-afbd-7a00b7f5c491&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=5212b25a118c463931caca50487af7094d4f1e50" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![