erate-results-within-chatgpt-063833672.html">OpenAI 的 DALL-E 3</a>文本到图像人工智能系统提供支持，该公司此前表示，该系统“明显更好”，能够通过您输入的文本提示掌握您想要实现的最终产品。DALL -E 3 的设计还旨在更好地渲染前代产品遇到困难的元素，例如人手。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>这是微软自<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-rebrands-its-ai-powered-bing-chat-as-copilot-160027250.html?_fsig=RkNWieP1tvOmHMwk_O9uHg--%7EA">更名</a>为 Bing Chat 以来发布的最新 Copilot 产品。该公司还将Copilot带到<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsofts-copilot-ai-is-officially-coming-to-windows-10-180020032.html?_fsig=inZmxSTB2MgSHuug08nx6Q--%7EA">Windows 10</a> ，然后将Windows 11带到<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-bet-big-on-ai-in-2023-but-its-ai-future-is-still-unclear-143055721.html?_fsig=inZmxSTB2MgSHuug08nx6Q--%7EA">Windows 11</a> ，该设备（基于平台的用户号码）访问了AI Chatbot的访问。有了这些移动推出，微软正在扩大副副总裁的范围，尤其是因为应用程序可以免费使用。</p>本文最初出现在Engadget上，网址为https://www.engadget.com/microsofts-copilot-copilot-ai-chatbot-arp-arp-arp-arp-arrives-arives-on-ios-112559129.html?src=rsss]>;]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/microsofts-copilot-ai-chatbot-app-arrives-on-ios-112559129.html?src=rss]]><source_id> Engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 1CEB8AB1-B46D-4DFF-A2E3-0C254759A0DC</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mariella Moon]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Sat, 30 Dec 2023 11:25:59 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1703935551</ingested><modified> 2023-12-30T11：26：00+00：00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="875" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F2c01cfc0-a6e2-11ee-bfbf-04a161880924&amp;resize=1400%2C875&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=fc95057c5aaba3d1e5792f31c1cda81287199fae" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="875" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F2c01cfc0-a6e2-11ee-bfbf-04a161880924&amp;resize=1400%2C875&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=ba148f0b9d8df549cc8444db387ce82add42b52e" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Microsoft]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Screenshots of a screen with text responses from AI.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Microsoft]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[From toilets to the sky: UK startup makes waste into low carbon jet fuel]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>英国一家公司<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:LinkedIn;elmt:;cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=6deefbf2-941b-4156-9f41-a61ebb50d13d&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=LinkedIn&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5saW5rZWRpbi5jb20vY29tcGFueS9maXJlZmx5LWdyZWVuLWZ1ZWxzLyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMzdmYWEzZjMtMWM1ZC00YzZiLWFkMzUtNjBlOGQyNDcwY2Q0In0&amp;signature=AQAAAYc0wN_IuEWs321ce919sp7bI0h6uKiqYEbJj6gF_Hf0&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fcompany%2Ffirefly-green-fuels%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.linkedin.com/company/firefly-green-fuels/"><ins>Firefly Green Fuels</ins></a>开发了一种新形式的喷气燃料，该燃料完全不含化石，由人类废物制成。根据<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-gloucestershire-67771640.amp"><ins>英国广播公司（BBC）的说法，</ins></a>该公司与克兰菲尔德大学（Cranfield University）的专家合作，确认他们开发的燃料的碳足迹比今天航空中使用的燃料低90％。独立监管机构的测试证实了萤火虫绿燃料的开发几乎与标准<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://flyfirefly.uk/what-how/"><ins>A1喷气燃料</ins></a>相同。</p><p> 2021年，该公司从运输部获得了200万英镑的赠款，以继续开发其可持续航空燃料。尽管该公司尚未在商业上可用，但<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://flyfirefly.uk/about-us/"><ins>该公司表示</ins></a>，它将其燃料带入全球市场，并将在5年内运营其第一家商业电厂。该公司已经与<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://flyfirefly.uk/wizz-air-invests-5m-in-firefly/"><ins>预算航空公司Wizz Air</ins></a>建立了合作伙伴关系 - 公司的名称及其潜在可燃物的来源几乎不可能是更完美的配对 - 从2028年开始为其提供燃料。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="1bb59480d6764de490cfb4b7468fb2c4"><iframe height="524" width="504" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen title="嵌入式柱"></iframe></div><p>它目前从英国的自来水公司那里采购废物，并通过称为水<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0960852414013911#:~:text=Hydrothermal%20liquefaction%20of%20biomass%20is,structure%20to%20mainly%20liquid%20components."><ins>热液化</ins></a>的工艺将精制的污水转换为污泥或原油。固体副产品也可以在作物肥料中制成。该公司声称，整个过程的<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.nationalgrid.com/stories/energy-explained/what-is-carbon-intensity#:~:text=Carbon%20intensity%20explained&amp;text=It%20refers%20to%20how%20many,generated%20creates%20CO2%20emissions."><ins>碳强度</ins></a>（衡量产生能源需要多少碳）为<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://flyfirefly.uk/what-how/"><ins>7.97克</ins></a>二氧化碳二氧化碳（GCO²E/MJ）。相比之下， <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://theicct.org/sites/default/files/publications/Alt-aviation-fuel-sustainability-mar2021.pdf"><ins>ICCT表示，</ins></a>喷气燃料范围为85至95GCO²E/MJ的碳强度。</p><p>正如该<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://flyfirefly.uk/about-us/"><ins>公司指出的</ins></a>那样，有机物需要数百万年的时间才能开发成动力汽车和飞机的化石燃料。 Firefly的解决方案可以在几天之内产生燃料 - 更重要的是，人类废物是广泛可用的资源。目前尚不清楚可持续喷气燃料是否比目前可用的燃料更便宜。无法立即联系该公司发表评论。但是，在一份声明中，该公司的<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://flyfirefly.uk/making-saf-from-sewage/"><ins>首席执行官詹姆斯·海格特（James Hygate）</ins></a>提到，使用人类废物是“便宜而丰富的原料（该原料）永远不会用完”。</p><p>在我们的空间中实现碳中立性一直是<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/europe-is-planning-to-label-flights-according-to-their-carbon-footprint-093055032.html"><ins>欧洲和美国</ins></a>领导人的长期目标。虽然<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ev-buyers-will-get-an-instant-rebate-for-every-car-purchased-starting-in-2024-211224909.html"><ins>电动汽车</ins></a>在汽车行业取得了进展，但我们可能还需要一段时间才能看到<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/we-wont-have-electric-airplanes-until-battery-tech-improves-160058357.html"><ins>电池供电的商业飞机</ins></a>。因此，与此同时，欢迎创建更环保的喷气燃料的解决方案。</p>本文最初发表在https://www.engadget.com/from-toilets-to-the-sky-uk-startup-makes-waste-waste-into-low-carbon-jet-jet-fuel-194003678.html？ = rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/from-toilets-to-the-sky-uk-startup-makes-waste-into-low-carbon-jet-fuel-194003678.html?src=rss]]><source_id> Engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 37FAA3F3-1C5D-4C6B-AD35-60E8D2470CD4 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Malak Saleh]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 29 Dec 2023 19:40:03 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1703878804</ingested><modified> 2023-12-29T19：40：10+00：00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Airline Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[Environment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Nature & Environment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Malak Saleh]]></category><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F7776e790-a680-11ee-b7f0-c951c06cbf9c&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=f584b6c011a777b20cc27ac925b7716ace4610c8" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F7776e790-a680-11ee-b7f0-c951c06cbf9c&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=200eaa79d651bbfb80d43f16ddd72b238a22273a" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Ground service before flight. Refueling of airplane at airport.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Refueling of airplane]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[NVIDIA nerfed its RTX 4090 graphics card for Chinese buyers, thanks to US export rules]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/29/24018799/nvidia-4090d-china-slower-us-sanctions"><ins>正如</ins><em><ins>《 Verge》</ins></em>报道的那样，</a> NVIDIA将发布专门针对中国市场<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.nvidia.cn/geforce/graphics-cards/40-series/rtx-4090-d/"><ins>的GeForce RTX 4090图形卡的低功率版本</ins></a>。 RTX 4090D已经在公司的中国网站上拥有一个产品页面，其CUDA核心少于其名称的堂兄。它还具有较低的425W而不是450W的功率吸引力。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-launches-new-gaming-chip-china-comply-with-us-export-controls-2023-12-29/"><ins>据</ins><em><ins>路透社报道，这两个版本之间的大多数规格保持不变，但是在游戏和使用创意应用程序时，CUDA核心和降低功率的降低速度降低了5％。</ins></em></a>即使有性能下降，NVIDIA仍然说4090D是“性能，效率和人工智能驱动图形的量子飞跃”。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>这都是由于美国对运往中国和俄罗斯的高端计算机芯片的出口限制，以试图遏制这两个国家开发可用于武器制造和监视等应用的技术。这些规则<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nvidia-government-rule-restricting-export-ai-chips-china-russia-061846437.html?_fsig=z2L0ZlSgS6oqhw9luRLNZQ--%7EA"><ins>于2022年宣布，</ins></a>但今年正式制定，使像Nvidia这样的制造商争先恐后地找到了满足中国消费者和美国监管机构需求的解决方案。</p><p>我们知道，由于限制阻止其出售原始的RTX 4090和AI相关的GPU，因此该公司<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nvidia-may-soon-announce-new-ai-chips-for-china-to-get-around-us-export-restrictions-100509873.html"><ins>将专门为中国大规模市场制作新芯片</ins></a>。 NVIDIA表示，最新的GPU“旨在完全遵守美国政府的出口控制”，并补充说，在整个筹码的开发过程中，它“与美国政府广泛互动”。</p><p> RTX 4090D将于1月的某个时候在整个中国提供，价格为12,999或约1,836美元左右。这应该有助于减少该国对强大图形卡的需求，因为<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.tomshardware.com/news/chinese-factories-add-blowers-to-old-rtx-4090-cards">据报道，上述限制已导致工厂重新利用工厂</a>，以专注于AI加速器而不是被禁止的RTX 4090。</p>本文最初发表在https://www.engadget.com/nvidia-nerfed-its-rtx-4090-graphics-card-for-for-chinese-buyers-thanks-thanks-to-us-export-rules-190621145.html ？src = rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/nvidia-nerfed-its-rtx-4090-graphics-card-for-chinese-buyers-thanks-to-us-export-rules-190621145.html?src=rss]]><source_id> Engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 0057767E-80​​CA-478D-88FB-13099A08E822</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawrence Bonk]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 29 Dec 2023 19:06:21 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1703876782</ingested><modified> 2023-12-29T19：06：33+00：00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[la